Description: Retro DJ to Go, LLC is a company offering disc jockey services to parties, weddings and large group events.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Houston Area, Southern US
Full Description: Retro DJ to Go provides Houston and surrounding areas with DJ's for Weddings, Corporate Events, Themed Parties, School Dances, Private Parties and more.  We are your full service mobile disc jockey company specializing in high end, high profile events! The co-owners of Retro DJ to Go began as event DJ's in college working for a small mobile disc jockey company. After years of performing at private parties, weddings, corporate events, galas, fundraisers, sorority/fraternity parties, fashion shows and many other events, they moved on to working for a pro audio company that specialized in providing sound reinforcement for concerts and large events in the area. Eventually both became club headliners and competed against each other at various clubs in the area and even on radio. In 2006, one of the co-owners was getting married and used the in house wedding facility DJ.  What a mistake!  The DJ did nothing but play music. He could not even talk on the mic. There was no coordination of events and nothing was setup for the photographer (a key to the success of any wedding). We couldn't take it anymore and took over the event and turned it into a huge success!  In 2007, Retro DJ to Go was formed as it was clear that Houston had a need for quality event DJ's. Retro DJ to Go specializes in all event types and staff's five of the best trained DJ's in the industry. Every DJ hired goes through a rigorous on boarding process that includes programming, beat matching, event organization, and MC'ing.  We are Houston's premier DJ service and it shows in every event we perform.
Industry Groups: Media and Entertainment, Music and Audio

Description: Valgrind is an instrumentation framework for building dynamic analysis tools.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Boston Area, East Coast, New England
Full Description: Valgrind is an instrumentation framework for building dynamic analysis tools. There are Valgrind tools that can automatically detect many memory management and threading bugs, and profile your programs in detail. You can also use Valgrind to build new tools. The Valgrind distribution currently includes six production-quality tools: a memory error detector, two thread error detectors, a cache and branch-prediction profiler, a call-graph generating cache and branch-prediction profiler, and a heap profiler. It also includes three experimental tools: a stack/global array overrun detector, a second heap profiler that examines how heap blocks are used, and a SimPoint basic block vector generator. It runs on the following platforms: X86/Linux, AMD64/Linux, ARM/Linux, ARM64/Linux, PPC32/Linux, PPC64/Linux, PPC64LE/Linux, S390X/Linux, MIPS32/Linux, MIPS64/Linux, TILEGX/Linux, X86/Solaris, AMD64/Solaris, ARM/Android (2.3.x and later), ARM64/Android, X86/Android (4.0 and later), MIPS32/Android, X86/Darwin and AMD64/Darwin.

Headquarters Regions: Greater San Diego Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: We are a Real Estate Software solution that offers Real Estate Agents a platform to receive inbound requests from people looking to Buy or Sell a home. Our software provides a CRM that Agents can SMS, Email, Send VM and utilize AI & Machine Learning based client-qualification in order to nurture prospects into commissions.  Think of this way, if you are a guy in his 30's who is a Republican and you enjoy Football -- your team is the Chargers for example. Then our algorithm will match you with an Agent who shares these traits and interests and has a successful track record in your desired Zip Code and Home Type, including Price Point.  The Agent we match you with, will have a system to send you homes and updates the entire time through our App that easily connects both parties -- without the need to download the iOS/android app as the mobile version suffices.  We charge the Agent $0-20 per successful match and we take 20-30% of the Commission the Agent earns while providing incentives back to the buyer.  We Generate over 20,000 referrals per month and successfully match over 50% of them  Our growth is ready for 100% matching -- we just need more Agents to be aware we exist
